{"id": "1434615443221647370", "channel_id": "1434615443221647370", "type": 0, "author_id": "204796527930114048", "author_name": ".saltynacl", "author_bot": false, "content": "As in have the bars on the left display somewhere (or at least be easily accessible) in the menu in the right. I'm sure people probably start remembering what good stats are, but as someone who doesn't know the numbers yet it's tedious to go back and forth between menus to make sure I'm not throwing away anything good.", "timestamp": "2025-11-02T18:49:35.530000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-02T18:52:43.609000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1434615443569770689", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 150894, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434615443221647370/1434615443569770689/image.png?ex=69cc173f&is=69cac5bf&hm=a3cc58074255b355a9f70a010c1753ba408a7b09388c10d0c814c01e07021a55&"}, {"id": "1434615444538527825", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1610618, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434615443221647370/1434615444538527825/image.png?ex=69cc173f&is=69cac5bf&hm=10db5b04e6215c837ec805a954483b2db0b4ff0d49ecd4a02882bef460b02de8&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434615443221647370", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Would it be possible to show transcription quality in the covenant dismantle UI?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1434619115024154765", "channel_id": "1434615443221647370", "type": 0, "author_id": "233874560682950656", "author_name": "wolfierce", "author_bot": false, "content": "until there's a solution, max stats:\nAliemus 0.8\nSigil 1.2%\nAmplification 1.6%\nCrit rate 1.6%\nCrit DMG 2.4%\nKeyflare 2.4\nRealm 4\nDeath Res 5.6%", "timestamp": "2025-11-02T19:04:10.956000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434615443221647370", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Would it be possible to show transcription quality in the covenant dismantle UI?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
